<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/21757207">怎么能马上救一个素不相识的想自杀的人？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="883889" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">希望今后的日子我们都能好好为自己生活^_^，哪怕波浪滔天</div>


